      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite and version-controlled release process consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 is used under a validated installation qualification (IQ/OQ) procedure. The solver version is locked in the project configuration management system. Regression test suite covers 47 canonical flow cases including rotating machinery. SQA documentation reviewed and confirmed compliant with MRL 2 expectations."
    },
