    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment matrix. Validation evidence from the multi-site hemolysis data collection study demonstrates MAPE of 8.3% against the RH acceptance criterion, well within the 15% threshold. CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the defined COU.",
